arb, an open-source multiphysics finite volume solver
originally written by Dalton Harvie (daltonh@unimelb.edu.au), this is now a public collaborative project

* to run the solver you use the ./arb script
* try ./arb --help to list available options
* to get going, look at the readme file in the examples/tutorial_1 directory or at the manual in the doc directory
